<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
<h2>About</h2>
<h4><strong>Coupon Dispenser</strong> is a tool to distribute single-use discount codes to buyers of products.
    <br /> <br />
    <strong>How it Works</strong> <br />Sellers register and create offers, and add discount codees for each offer.
Buyers sign up for offers and get a discount code.
Sellers promote their products and build email lists of buyers.
    <br /> <br />
<strong>Features</strong> <br />
System supports single seller company or multiple sellers.
Email confirmation assures real, interested buyers.
JSON API for accessing the discount code distribution tool from any landing page.
    <br /> <br />
    <strong>Web Hosting</strong> <br />
    Easily host site from Microsoft Azure cloud platform.</h4>
